Following the EOF specific tests suggestion:
the simple vectors format that will check if the given eof code valid or not 
generatable with t8n 
```

"Filler"
{
    "testname" : 
    {
        "data" : [
            ":raw 0xeof",
            ":label code :raw 0xeof2"
        ],
        "expect" : [
            {
                "indexes" : {
                        "data" : -1
                },
                "network" : [">=Berlin"],
                "result" : true
            }
        ]
    }
}

"Test"
{
    "testname" : 
    [
        {
            "index" : "0",
            "code" : "0xeof0",
            "results" : 
            {
                "Berlin" : false,
                "Shanghai" : true
            }
        },
        {
            "index" : "1",
            "code" : "0xeof2",
            "results" : 
            {
                "Berlin" : false,
                "Shanghai" : false
            }
        }
    ]
}
```
